Bug Reporting:
If you encounter bugs please feel free to reach out and file a report!
You can file them on github and I'll get to them when I get to them.

Known bugs: (might fix)
if you have a ~/.ldshrc file, and decide to include PS1 and alias there, if PS1 comes before alias it won't work.
(not too sure about any others, please report them if you find any)
